      • toDataBuffers

        public static BodyExtractor<reactor.core.publisher.Flux<DataBuffer>,ReactiveHttpInputMessage> toDataBuffers()
        Return a BodyExtractor that returns the body of the message as a Flux of DataBuffers.

        Note that the returned buffers should be released after usage by calling DataBufferUtils.release(DataBuffer)

        Returns:
        a BodyExtractor that returns the body
